{"tid":1506002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(輿論戰) 聽日所有phone-in節目一定要大家幫手","createTime":"2019-08-25T16:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T01:53:12.000Z","uid":19513,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc680e51885bbc21c539114a37c1ec071f5f37d","tid":1506002,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"經過今晚，Cctvb剩係放大藍衫被打、墨汁人、汽油彈、開槍同埋麻雀館既事。<br />\n<br />\n聽日phone-in要比大家一個好既approach ，大家都知香港人幾善忘，唔好比人spin去其他位，事情既因果原由就唔見哂！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住自己既身份，同埋想講既要點！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n0800-1000 香港電台第一台<br />\n千禧年代 / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n1700-1800 香港電台第一台<br />\n自由風自由Phone / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n0630-0700, 0715-1000 雷霆881 (陳志雲版)<br />\n0800-1000 叱咤903 (潘小濤版)<br />\n在晴朗的一天出發 / Phone in 電話: 1872881 (陳) / 1872903 (潘)"},{"pid":"342816556b5095986c8716c7e3faaec3ab9a55f8","tid":1506002,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"自推20下屌"},{"pid":"338791c45aacff449d7fd50e826ecbd2ff17e4b3","tid":1506002,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b3fd2343a1490b2a7b70feebb68ad9de4c46c0f6","tid":1506002,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"45a04da9223b873971fe0c9cf30302966344a455","tid":1506002,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:21.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"aeec55b928e16f157ec74e37218c8a10e743016f","tid":1506002,"uid":19513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"2d2759d883c6cd5d323756a6bd465212b59c0427","tid":1506002,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d90774a1ae1d1601a31397c559be2d67b0f40442","tid":1506002,"uid":19513,"like":0,"di